
## Global parameters for simulation

GPUID 0 # 0-9 number
RandomSeed -1932780356 # (integer, use negative value if use current time)
UseAbsolutePath false
TotalThreads -1 #(Integer, use negative value for using optimized number of threads)
MaxHistoriesPerBatch 10000
Verbosity 0

## Data directories
ParentDir data/spotplan # parent directory of DICOM files
DicomDir plan # directory of the DICOM
logFilePath log

# Gantry number selection
GantryNum 1

## Phantom geometry in patient plan calculation by Chanil Jeon
## Phantom Dim ==> Pixel count of XYZ
## Phantom Unit ==> mm
## Phantom Position ==> Basic position is phantom center (-200, -200, -200)
## Y is the depth position in DICOM

## If you use phantom geometry, set true
UsingPhantomGeo true

## While you use phantom geometry, program with two centimeter mode can get exact 2 cm position slice dose
TwoCentimeterMode true

## Phantom information. Two centimeter mode overrides this setting (no effect).
PhantomDimX 180
PhantomDimY 180
PhantomDimZ 400
PhantomUnitX 1
PhantomUnitY 1
PhantomUnitZ 1
PhantomPositionX -90.0
PhantomPositionY -90.0
PhantomPositionZ -380.0

## Quantity to score
Scorer Dose # Dose is dose to water. We support dose to medium, dose to water, track-weighted LET, dose-weighted LET. Modification in environment is needed to add selection
SupressStd true
ReadStructure true
ROIName External

## Source parameters
SourceType FluenceMap
SimulationType perBeam
BeamNumbers 1
ParticlesPerHistory 0.0001 # Scale factor to select the number of primary particles

## Not implemented yet
ScoreToCTGrid true

## Output path
OutputDir data/output/spotplan_3090 # output directory
OutputFormat dcm # output format (raw, mhd, mha, npz)
OverwriteResults true
